2026-05-11T06:18:17.6226265Z 218            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-11T06:18:17.6227086Z 219            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-11T06:18:17.6227958Z 220            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-11T06:18:17.6228756Z 221            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-11T06:18:17.6281787Z 222            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
