2026-05-11T06:18:18.0007590Z 239            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0007910Z 240            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0008245Z 241            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0008583Z 242            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0008795Z 243            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0009166Z 244            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0009486Z 245            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0009811Z 246            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0010144Z 247            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
2026-05-11T06:18:18.0010292Z 248        -->
